item.dc:creator: @R.I.P_RSC R.I.P RSC
item.description:
@R.I.P_RSC wrote:

Actually it shouldnt matter from where you do it.

Try this: Go to My Computer-> right click-> Properties->Advanced->Environment
Variables->System variables and locate “PATH”. Add C:\windows\system32 at the
end if it is not already there.
